{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_02_02",
  "title": "井川葵 2話 遠慮なんていらない",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "愛に元気がないから、ちょっと話してあげてくれないか\nあぁすずは一番頼りになるから。ありがとう。じゃあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai isn’t doing so good. Could you have a word with her?\nYou’re the best‚ Suzu. Thanks. Bye.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.333333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6266.666666666667,
          "startTime": 11.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 11.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……随分あっさりと引き受けてくれたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…She took on the job easily enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ見えて\n面倒見がいいからな、すずは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You might not think it‚\nbut Suzu is great at taking care of others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.466666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 18.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "一番頼りになるとか言って\n持ち上げてたじゃないか。君も策士だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You even called her “the best.”\nYou know how to get your way‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.966666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや本当に頼りになるんだって\n明るいし、精神的にもタフなんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I meant it. You really can rely on her at times like this.\nShe’s cheerful and mentally quite tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 31.033333333333335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、いいのかな\n彼女を、僕達の、LizNoirの問題に巻き込んで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But are you sure about this?\nDragging her into our LizNoir problems?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 39.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "同じ事務所にはなったけど、彼女達にとって\n僕達はライバルでもある。申し訳ないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know we’re in the same agency now‚\nbut we’re still rivals. I’m sorry for the trouble.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 47.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "葵、初めてうちの子達――\nさくらと琴乃に会った日のことを覚えているか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ do you remember the first time you met them?\nSakura and Kotono. The first day you met them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、三枝さんに会いに行って\n二人に会ったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I went to see Mr. Saegusa\nand the two of them were there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 59.833333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "まだ、サニピも月ストも結成前だったんだっけ？\nあの頃は二人ともまだまだだったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wasn’t it before Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest were even formed?\nThey were still just starting out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 67.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、葵と莉央さんが彼女達の前で踊ってくれたろ\nあれは凄く刺激になったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You and Rio danced for them‚ didn’t you.\nThat really inspired them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それからだよ、二人がより一層レッスンに力を\n入れ出したのは。二人も、もちろん俺も感謝している",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They buckled down and worked even harder.\nI’m grateful for what for you did.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 84.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか\nでも、僕達は全然そんなつもりはなかったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.\nThat wasn’t really our intention.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "葵、君はとてもしっかりしている。自分の芯を持った\n強い子だ。でも、だからこそ覚えてほしいことがある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ you’ve got your act together. You have a strong core.\nBut I need you to remember something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 102.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "……何を？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "周りの人に、もっと頼っていいってことをだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s okay to rely on the people around you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "……周りの人に頼る……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rely on the people around me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.03333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 109.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、だから、今回のことは俺とすずに頼ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Like this. You can rely on Suzu and me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.53333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 114.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 127.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "……分かったよ。君とすずに期待させてもらう\n実は僕も彼女は嫌いじゃないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay. Let’s see what you two can do.\nI have to admit‚ I don’t hate her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "しゃべり方が面白い子だと思ってたら\n中身はもっと面白いからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The way she talks is funny‚\nbut the things she says are funny too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 136.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "葵の嫌いじゃない、は好きって意味だよな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you say you “don’t hate” someone‚ does that mean you like them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 141.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "……うるさいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Shut up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 145.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.93333333333337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "どうだい？　僕と莉央が考えた四人体制の新しい\n『The Last Chance』の振り付けだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think? Rio and I came up with\nthese new four-dancer moves for “The Last Chance.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "四人一緒じゃないから、分かりにくいかもだけど\n先に君の意見を聞きたいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It might be hard to tell without the four of us together‚\nbut I’d like to get your opinion on them first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "悪くないと思うけど、ソロのダンスパートは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not bad. What about the solo part?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "愛が前に出て、他のメンバーがサイドに回る\n新メンバーにそれぞれ見せ場があるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai comes forward‚ while the others drop to the sides.\nEach of the new members has a moment in the spotlight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "ファンの人達にもっと、愛とこころを知ってもらいたい\nそのための構成さ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We want the fans to get a better look at Ai and Kokoro.\nThat’s the main point of this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……そうか、優しい先輩だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… You’re a good senpai.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "……なんだか、不服そうだね\n言いたいことがあるなら、はっきり言ってくれないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You look a little disappointed.\nIf you have something to say‚ go ahead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "君と僕の間に遠慮なんていらない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t be shy with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、愛と莉央さんで前に出た方がよくないか？\nダンスのクオリティを重視すると、俺はそう感じるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. I think Ai and Rio should come forward together.\nThat's my feeling if you're emphasizing dance quality.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "……さすがだね\n実は僕もそう思ってたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Impressive.\nI was thinking the exact same thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "でも、愛にはもっと自信を持ってもらいたい\n自分はLizNoirのメンバーだと自覚してほしいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I want Ai to get a confidence boost.\nTo feel that she’s really a member of LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi021.m4a",
      "text": "彼女は僕達のバックダンサーじゃない\nもっと前に出てもらいたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s not just a back dancer for the rest of us.\nI want her to come to the front.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi022.m4a",
      "text": "だから、莉央と相談してあえてこの形にしたんだ\n莉央も納得してくれた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told Rio that I wanted to arrange it this way‚\nand she agreed as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "……君達の気持ちは分かる。けど、そういうのは\nLizNoirらしくないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I understand where you’re coming from.\nBut this doesn’t sound like LizNoir to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi023.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、君に指摘されて僕もそう思ったよ\n莉央に話して、構成を変える",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You know what. I actually agree.\nI’ll talk with Rio and make some changes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi024.m4a",
      "text": "また莉央とケンカかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hope we don’t end up fighting again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 247.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "言いにくいなら、俺が莉央さんに言おうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’re worried‚ I can handle telling her‚ if you like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 250.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi025.m4a",
      "text": "いや、今度、すずの別荘に合宿に行くし\nそこで、僕が言うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. We’ve got bootcamp at Suzu’s villa coming up.\nI’ll tell her there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 256.23333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi026.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスについて莉央に意見出来るのは\n僕くらいだからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m just about the only one who can give Rio pointers\nwhen it comes to dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 260.73333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、前にも言ったけど周りを\nもっと頼っていいんだぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you think so. Like I said before‚\nit’s okay to rely on others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.6666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_02-aoi027.m4a",
      "text": "……もう充分頼りにしてるよ、ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’ve relied on you plenty already‚ but thanks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 268.6333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}